        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span> badeend submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13936#pullrequestreview-4758381037\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Much less surprising default behavior <span aria-label=\"+1\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"+1\">:+1:</span> </p>\n</blockquote>",
